@startuml
title Factory Method

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Define an interface for creating an object; let subclasses decide which class to instantiate.

**Use when**: A class cannot anticipate the class of objects it must create, or wants to localize object creation.

**Key participants**: Creator, ConcreteCreator, Product, ConcreteProduct.
endlegend

interface Product

abstract class Creator {
  +factoryMethod() : Product
  +operation()
}

class ConcreteCreatorA
class ConcreteCreatorB

class ConcreteProductA
class ConcreteProductB

Creator <|-- ConcreteCreatorA
Creator <|-- ConcreteCreatorB

Product <|.. ConcreteProductA
Product <|.. ConcreteProductB

ConcreteCreatorA ..> ConcreteProductA : creates
ConcreteCreatorB ..> ConcreteProductB : creates
@enduml